        <font size="3"><big><big>(In face-to-face conversations, the meaning of a message
        is transported as follows [Mehrabian 1972]: 7% verbally, 38% para-verbally
        (intonation,
        volume) and 55% non-verbally (facial expression, gestures, body language))</big></big></font></big></font></font></big></p><big>
  </big></blockquote>
